{"tid":847623,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人弱智定香港MTR既指示牌唔清晰?","createTime":"2018-10-04T09:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T16:05:33.000Z","uid":35639,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4e54a3f6cbe1b4060973b3ae48df1e72a99df8","tid":847623,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"自問去唔同國家旅行,識唔識個種語言文字都好,係車站靠指示牌都搵到目的地<br />\n但偏偏係香港MTR,明明有中文指示,都俾大陸人問過不下20次邊度點去,問既人男女老幻都有<br />\n頭先仲離譜到係金鐘往荃灣月台問我荃灣搭邊架車<br />\n我點撚左佢搭藍色線往柴灣方向總站落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f381f5dd50688bef83b133fa8a22530f5064afe3","tid":847623,"uid":138557,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"大陸人唔係個個識字"},{"pid":"f78f35dc166db082317d9b4650ceba340d67af35","tid":847623,"uid":205865,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"男女老幻"},{"pid":"f8978ad5b0ecf59c64d0b57600e2b39a939997e2","tid":847623,"uid":176802,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"幻即係咩人?<br />\n<br />\n你睇到幻覺向你問路?"},{"pid":"7896090242cf5eda482390b2c4f7bc789e2728e1","tid":847623,"uid":50041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"D支那賤種根本就弱智，下下都塞撚住入閘機永遠唔可以順利入到，明明有個交叉符號係入閘機度又死拍爛拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9578bee000f4890eb6166c5d21dbbbac4926a1d","tid":847623,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"大陸人零舍多盲毛"},{"pid":"b833efd803d11bd8415164290e3e6532c21f1b6e","tid":847623,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"大陸人唔識字正常"},{"pid":"e51912e6bea994a73652a34ca1245175791848d1","tid":847623,"uid":7638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"屌